{"tid":1401892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚟緊拉人係警察最大目標 求下大家唔好比人拉","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:54:41.000Z","uid":53321,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a806af364926117ec9497219749c2277abb7e7","tid":1401892,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"求下大家一定要做好保護措施。<br />\n唔係淨係前線，係所有人，由出門口到返屋企都要保持警惕。<br />\n唔係要散水，但請大家要有隨時可能要離開既心態。<br />\n定一個行動既可行既目標，做到就收手，好冇？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58376f5ec0d10539813fa7b38aa0c160c7fa2e5a","tid":1401892,"uid":53321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"希望手足好好照顧好自己<br />\n將「不被捕」既重要性提高<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9f8d177e5f8ff3d0b716ae73d90b85e56fe177","tid":1401892,"uid":53321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:20:58.000Z","msg":"每見到有任何一個手足被捕都好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a8f0bd252c76c760c7dadab62cad7416821785","tid":1401892,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:21:29.000Z","msg":"你地係我鍾意呢個香港既原因<br />\n唔好令呢個原因消失 好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbc1fa66f6e6584738a5a70e3cc49b39aae78e6","tid":1401892,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:21:57.000Z","msg":"心痛"},{"pid":"4caf5a25e546a923b228aa8a163fc62d9e494375","tid":1401892,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4fe89af319a8b86246e9e654d35a0193383c0e","tid":1401892,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:25:45.000Z","msg":"搞完大龍鳳<br />\n啲狗上晒裝 乜野人都拉唔到<br />\n咁先最谷氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d148f2dd7126cdef0c2cad13925eb78952a3f608","tid":1401892,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}